summary: Racemenu preset I threw together to look similar to a certain character.
descriptionHtml:
I borrowed Breton Preset v7.0 from Fair Skin Complexion and in a few minutes turned her into this.

I'm using the maximum amount of mods, so I'm not sure exactly what she's wearing.

However, she definitely has:
Fair Skin Complexion
Vilja in Skyrim (Eyes)

CBBE body, Breton race, 0.88 height, 0.05 weight
Hair is "Butterfly" from KS Hairdos
author: WonderboyandYoungNastyMan
